{"tid":460882,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得80年代有個明星叫簡慧真","createTime":"2017-11-07T05:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T00:02:44.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"11b3af87113a856dd6243a61b4377c6f95a2bb37","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢有d似當年陳嘉玲 原來咁後生就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266484.jpg&h=b034955d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡慧真（1969年－1999年8月16日），香港女演員，出生於馬來西亞檳城。曾與李小龍之子李國豪合作演出《龍在江湖》，兩人甚為好友。也演出不少知名電影，例如《霸王花》系列、《英雄本色2》。後來簡慧真經常頭疼之故，1997年被檢查發現罹患腦癌，之後曾動過數次手術治療，但不久再度復發[1]。1999年7月24日上午，簡慧真突發全身痙攣，被緊急送至伊利沙伯醫院救治[1]。由於病情惡化，該年8月16日下午二時，簡慧真病逝於伊利沙伯醫院，得年30歲"},{"pid":"41a2baee2e66b14b92a0ef2ad6400635ef61c722","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://is.gd/awFKBn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FawFKBn&d=AyFUqcmf7VqkdZxnFZPfdk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=afab831a\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/awFKBn</a><br />\n曾與李國豪合作演出的《龍在江湖》。"},{"pid":"cd202280ad7c4e0f75576723d13d2016fe312dc2","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"說起簡慧真，最多的大概是很漂亮，有一種清純玉女的感覺。她出生在馬拉西亞，父親是巨商，16歲獲得「陽光小姐」冠軍，後來正式進入娛樂圈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2b8tcvu/roq0004s58rrqo16081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2b8tcvu%2Froq0004s58rrqo16081.jpg&h=82a26a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來到香港之後，首先和簡慧真結識的是李國豪，二人因為《龍在江湖》相遇，並因為都是混血兒的身份很要好，當簡慧真聽到李國豪暴斃的消息後，泣不成聲，以至於不能繼續採訪。"},{"pid":"83879aa294d0998258475e9d46fbeeb4b8dd9b46","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"後來又在《英雄本色2》中同張國榮搭戲，這部影片在香港上映期間一個小時內售清所有午夜場票，香港總票房為22,727,369.00港幣，在同年上映的《A計劃續集》中簡慧真也的戲份。<br />\n<br />\n後來在《霸王花》和《神勇飛虎霸王花》中的出色演出，更是使得她此後聲名鵲起，在香港名聲大噪。但這種火紅的影視生涯並沒有持續很久，在1993年以後，簡慧真便退出了娛樂圈，也正是在這一年李國豪死亡。"},{"pid":"df2897cdf691d8b65607aa8f1431842c9c40c9a4","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"《義膽雄心》更是讓大家見到了一個開朗活潑的領家女孩的形象，她愛笑，而這種笑又讓人覺得很單純、無邪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她是讓劉德華痴戀的混血兒美女<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3cvqa9j/rp300067psn48710n04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3cvqa9j%2Frp300067psn48710n04.jpg&h=59095d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在很多我們今天看來非常經典的影視作品，如今回過頭再看看那些當年曾經在我們難以忘懷的作品中留下身影，也已經是物是人非了。內地如此，港台也是如此，比如簡慧真，這位昔日的美艷女星，早已是離開了我們。"},{"pid":"a8fe7ee28c9c63a1b7933be3bbc695e33397ddad","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"比如在1987年，曾與成龍、張曼玉、劉嘉玲等一起出演了《A計劃續集》，簡慧真在其中出演那個邀請張曼玉和關之琳、劉嘉玲三位美女參加生日宴會的將軍的女兒，儘管戲份不多，但給人留下了深刻印象，也非常符合其千金大小姐的身份和定位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266489.jpg&h=2b31808c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266490.jpg&h=23058fe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e86a5088b7515f09440ec1611d064e4dacc0fa45","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"還曾出演由周潤發、張國榮等主演的電影《英雄本色2》，以及由胡慧中主演的《霸王花》系列，在其中都有精彩的表現。在劉德華主演的《義膽雄心》中，曾經還使得劉德華對其非常痴迷，在戲中她扮演劉德華養父的女兒仙迪，和劉德華上演了一段忘我的戀情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266491.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266491.jpg&h=efaf8f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266492.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266492.jpg&h=61208899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266493.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266493.jpg&h=ad8a8807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/42/4266494.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F42%2F4266494.jpg&h=a74f811e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"585e4d0736c3386935aa73411c914e3ed6aed004","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"當紅時，簡慧真退隱經商。但不幸的是，這位美艷女星在1998年患了腦癌，第二年就去世了，年僅31歲。據說，簡慧真在治病期間，表現的非常堅強，沒有絲毫的怨言和悲哀之情。簡慧真的英年早逝，實在令人感到惋惜"},{"pid":"3130732e1a4663d8da819ccc9bb1ea168d28a084","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係冇人識佢 我睇過嗰套霸王花 第一次都覺得望落似陳嘉玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dc154afd2f88d25721e34b87c8d8aaf0136d41","tid":460882,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"有啲印象"},{"pid":"141091d79c9f1137044fda30d076c1c9805236d3","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲印象</blockquote><br />\n邊套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481a1b9ebaf467e2b31188e7d11c94bcd14ce63f","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"佢可能係暗星 走左都冇人識<br />\n就算紅過一排都冇人會記得"},{"pid":"7a8d2642dba1cdbbc8396941f5325e2b522a3824","tid":460882,"uid":38407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"G妹係80年代出世？😮"},{"pid":"b243f544f4e5fd2baa748221e60f870f26079ecf","tid":460882,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T00:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>G妹係80年代出世？😮</blockquote><br />\n因為我以前煲開舊片 咁咪知有依個人囉姊😊"}]}